Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-haystack`, instrumenting the Haystack
(`haystack-ai`) `Pipeline.run` and `AsyncPipeline.run_async` entry points and
emitting a standard GenAI workflow span (`invoke_workflow`) via
`opentelemetry-util-genai`. Set
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental` to capture the
experimental content-carrying attributes.
